OL,8,Fof the year for delivery drivers
OL,9,Facross Wales as the countdown to
OL,10,FChristmas gets underway.
OL,12,FAnd South Wales Police is urging van
OL,13,Fdrivers to be vigilant after several
OL,14,Frecent incidents of theft around
